OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779289870
OL,3,CImages show wreckage as two men
OL,4,Csentenced for racing on road
OL,6,FTwo men have been sentenced for racing
OL,7,Feach other on a Sussex road.
OL,9,FSussex Police released images showing
OL,10,Fthe wreckage of a Vauxhall Corsa
OL,11,Fdriven by Miller Watts, 20, of
OL,12,FSkinners Lane, Catsfield.
OL,14,FWatts crashed into a tree and
OL,15,Ffractured his skull, after racing a
OL,16,FToyota Yaris driven by Charlie Young,
OL,17,F20, of Lilac Lane, Stone Cross.
OL,19,FThe incident occurred on the A271 near
OL,20,FBattle - a 60mph single carriageway -
OL,21,Fon the evening of 3 March 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
