PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779289870
OL,3,CImages show wreckage as two men
OL,4,Csentenced for racing on road
OL,6,FThe Corsa, driven by Watts, struck a
OL,7,Ftree on a bend. Its engine was
OL,8,Fdiscovered 50 metres away, such was
OL,9,Fthe force of the impact.
OL,11,FThe Corsa's speedometer was found to
OL,12,Fbe locked out at 86mph.
OL,14,FWatts and Young were charged with
OL,15,Fdangerous driving and both men
OL,16,Fsubsequently pleaded guilty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
