FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779289870
OL,3,CImages show wreckage as two men
OL,4,Csentenced for racing on road
OL,6,FThey appeared before Hastings
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on April 27, where
OL,8,Fthey were both given a 12-month
OL,9,Fcommunity order, requiring them to
OL,10,Fcomplete 120 hours of unpaid work.
OL,12,FThey were also disqualified from
OL,13,Fdriving for 12 months and ordered to
OL,14,Fpay #199 in court costs.
OL,16,FThey must take an extended re-test if
OL,17,Fthey want to drive again.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
