PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779289870
OL,3,CImages show wreckage as two men
OL,4,Csentenced for racing on road
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, PC Steve
OL,7,FKimber, of the Roads Policing Unit,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our roads are designed to
OL,9,Fenable motorists to get from A to B;
OL,10,Fthey are not designed to be used as a
OL,11,Frace track.
OL,13,F"Doing so can lead to devastating
OL,14,Fconsequences, and it's extremely
OL,15,Ffortunate neither of the drivers - nor
OL,16,Fany other innocent road users - were
OL,17,Fkilled or seriously injured in this
OL,18,Fcase.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
