OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779289870
OL,3,CImages show wreckage as two men
OL,4,Csentenced for racing on road
OL,6,F"Speeding is one of the most common
OL,7,Fcauses of fatal and serious injury
OL,8,Fcollisions, and this sort of behaviour
OL,9,Fwill absolutely not be tolerated.
OL,11,F"The fact that both drivers must take
OL,12,Fan extended re-test should they wish
OL,13,Fto drive again demonstrates their
OL,14,Fclear ignorance to road safety.
OL,16,F"I hope they can learn from this
OL,17,Fmistake to ensure they improve the
OL,18,Fsafety of themselves and others."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
